Get Connected.Get Results.
McGraw-Hill Connect is a digital teaching and learning environment that saves students and instructors time while improving performance over a variety of critical outcomes.
See for Yourself




Get Connected.Get LearnSmart Advantage.
Designed to maximize productivity and efficiency in learning, LearnSmart creates high impact study sessions and is proven to improve grades.  
Learn More




Get Connected.Get Integrated.
Connect seamlessly integrates with every learning management system out there, so you can easily combine your course resources into a single platform.
Learn More




Get Connected.Get Engaged.
With our media rich eBook, course content comes alive with videos, interactive elements, and even the instructor's own notes.
Learn More




Get Connected.Get Tegrity.
Capture your lectures for students. Easy access outside of class anytime, anywhere, on just about any device.
Learn More




Get Connected.Stay Connected.
From in site tutorials, to tips and best practices, to live help from colleagues and specialists – you're never left alone to maximize Connect's potential.
Learn More















Proven Effective

Grade Distribution
See More Proof




Tailored To You
Connect's rich content, abundant assignment types, and flexible policy options can be customized, while its powerful study tools adapt to individual student understanding and need. Simply put, Connect offers everything you need to reach your goals, your way.Learn More


