McGraw-Hill Education, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 1:24 PM ET
Media

Company Overview of McGraw-Hill Education, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
McGraw-Hill Education, Inc. offers educational materials and learning solutions worldwide. The company operates through Higher Education, K – 12, International, Professional, and Other segments. It offers instructional content, adaptive learning, assessment, and institutional services to students, professors, provosts, and presidents in the college, university, and postgraduate markets; educational resources to elementary and secondary schools in digital and print formats; content and subscription-based information services for the professional business, medical, technical, and education/test prep communities, including professionals preparing for entry into graduate programs; and internatio...
McGraw-Hill Education, Inc. offers educational materials and learning solutions worldwide. The company operates through Higher Education, K – 12, International, Professional, and Other segments. It offers instructional content, adaptive learning, assessment, and institutional services to students, professors, provosts, and presidents in the college, university, and postgraduate markets; educational resources to elementary and secondary schools in digital and print formats; content and subscription-based information services for the professional business, medical, technical, and education/test prep communities, including professionals preparing for entry into graduate programs; and international products to serve educational and professional markets. The company’s products and services are available in more than 60 languages. McGraw-Hill Education, Inc. is based in New York, New York.
Detailed Description


